  ("npc9_intro", "You there, good {reg59?woman:man}. Be so kind as to fetch me another drink, eh?"), #Clovis
  ("npc10_intro", "God thee mid sie, {reg59?madame:sir}! Here's to the doom and downfall of all Welsh!"), #Ceawlin
  ("npc11_intro", "Heill, {reg59?my pretty:handsome}. I've been watching you a while."), #Solveig
