  ("npc3_intro_response_1", "Calm down. I intend you no harm. Why are you so afraid?"), #Brunhild
  ("npc4_intro_response_1", "You're not very talkative, are you?"), #Donnchadh
  ("npc5_intro_response_1", "Certainly. With whom do I have the pleasure of drinking?"), #Morgant
