  ("npc7_intro_response_1", "My apologies. I was merely going to say that you look a bit down on your luck."), #Dwywei
  ("npc8_intro_response_1", "Merely to pass the time of day, foreigner, if you're not otherwise engaged."), ##Reginhard , frisio
