  ("npc11_intro_response_1", "Who are you, and why are you watching me?"), #Solveig
  ("npc12_intro_response_1", "So nice to meet you."), #Asbjorn
  ("npc13_intro_response_1", "To pass the time of day with a fellow traveler, if you permit."),  #Swedish, Helgi
  ("npc14_intro_response_1", "Um... I don't think so."), #Ailchu
  ("npc15_intro_response_1", "I am. What concern is it of yours, may I ask?"),#Agasicles
  ("npc16_intro_response_1", "Are you tongue-tied?"), #Beda

  ("npc1_intro_response_2", "Yes, I know that he wants you to join me, but I do not need you. Farewell."), #Caio
  ("npc2_intro_response_2", "I have better things to do."), #Egil
  ("npc3_intro_response_2", "Run along now, girl. I have real work to do -- not whatever it is you fear I'll do."), #Brunhild
  ("npc4_intro_response_2", "No."), ##Donnchadh
